Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the first science of truth then. We also have the first science of international diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:01:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been corrected since Canada. Canada is about 415, right about here. So, here's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,America at 421. Here is another citizenry, another country. As I say, you have to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the people, the government, and the ruler. It will first give you the first science of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,diplomatic relationships. I see nothing but really profound ignorance in international
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,relationships in which the people are addressing each other completely incorrectly, no appeal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,turning each other off, trying to sell them a program that to them is horrific. You have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to know who you're talking to, who you're talking to. When a patient goes into my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't expect them to come from where I'm in after 50 years of psychiatry and psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to where they are. He doesn't even know he's addicted yet. Five DWIs, the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,wife has left him, he's lost his job, three times in jail. What do you mean I got an alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,problem, doc? So, help me God, they say that. Five times in jail, wife's lost, he's bankrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he's unemployable, they've taken the keys to his car away, he was just in six months
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for driving without a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He sits there and tells me he don't have an alcohol problem. Okay, so, let's talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,international diplomacy because world peace is very profoundly important. In history,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,peace has prevailed only seven percent of civilized time. Seven percent. So, stop lamenting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:03:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,war, get real. War is the reality, peace is the unreality. War has prevailed ninety-three
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Three percent of the time. Only seven percent. Everybody was broke and tired or what. Liquor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was free for a few years. I don't know, they all got smashed into the hell with fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say peace is the anomaly, isn't it? It's an unnatural condition, statistically
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,unlikely condition. Occurs only seven percent of the history of civilization. Here's America
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,at 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to speak with another country? You've got to know where they're at. You've
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,got to know where they're at. Here's what America does. It talks across this way. There's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody there at 421 except you folks. You're talking in a mirror. Democracy is the wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world, yeah, right. And what does the mirror say back to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's egoistic self, that's ego cynicism. Aren't we wonderful? Well, then my second question
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and aren't we wonderful, just has not sold, folks, hasn't sold. Even where it prevailed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's disappeared, replaced by secular socialism. Even where it did work, it's disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so at 421, you've got to know who you're talking about. Canada at 415, Canada has
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,also gone secular socialist. You've got to wait three months to get an appointment with a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't want to vote for it. South America, you see in the high 300s. I've been in Argentina
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and Brazil, very energetic people, I'll tell you. Like in China or Korea, you're dealing with people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that are very energetic, very on the go, very upbeat. Here you got China at 310. Here you got
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuba, the government of Cuba, and then you've got the people of Cuba. The leader of Cuba is about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,here. The people of Cuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,are still up in the 300s. Something else we saw in China. So the leader of a country may be very
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous. I'm thinking of one who calibrated so high, I said, man, this is going to be great for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the future of the world. And the people calibrated in the 300s. They're swell people. It's great to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,go on a vacation there. The government is totally rotten. You don't dare drive your car there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave your car at the border. Let's see, the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The bureaucracy of the government I'm holding in mind calibrates over 160, 165, about 160.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you've got a great president, you've got great people, and the government calibrates it at 160.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Violated, you get held for ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Trumped up charges, they find out you got money, you stay in the jail until you get your money up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you've got great disparity between the people, the leader, and the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See the same thing in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,China once calibrated about 140, it's up to 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can own property there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,President Zhang, J-H-A-N-G, what was his name, calibrated about 450.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Very smart guy, wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with the country then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Same thing in post-communist Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't see people exuberant freedom, you saw the white, what do they call it, mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the Russian mafia take over, because the government was rotting through and through, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here you see Central Africa, the calibrations in Jordan and various places are as low as 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Life expectancy is about 4 1⁄2 years, more than half the people are born with AIDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't die of starvation and AIDS, then a warring chieftain of a neighboring tribe will chop you up into small pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They literally chop each other up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop each other up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you die by chop up, AIDS and starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop them up is getting to be stylish, it's on TV lately, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how primitive and barbaric it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the implications for the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this our president?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this our government?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And look who we're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a country with a booming economy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing Nixon did is China could have been a real foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dynamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put Chinamen, what is it, a thousand abreast and start them walking around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they will never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As the leading Chinese get to this side, the population has already increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can encircle this people with the population forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a giant problem they could have been if that antagonism had remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we did was we cracked that egg and we became trading partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now a trading partnership is meaningful, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Democracy is not meaningful up here to these people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now China is not going to make war with us ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're their biggest customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality succeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:09:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here, people want to know, what do we get from dealing with you, paying attention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to your diplomats and your high-sounding, highfalutin philosophy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a huge economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So China makes so much money dealing with us, they will never be, you realize how close
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,China came to really being the ultimate, forget about Russia, put China together, they could
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,have defeated the United States, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One against one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we're dealing with countries that are in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want to sell democracy, tell people what it can do for your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What it can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not how wonderful it is, how superior it is, but how does it serve your needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My understanding of addiction is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't help him get sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to somehow meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet him where he's living, to provide him with something that appeals to him, that now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,he would listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I say, go to AA or something like that, everything else is hopeless, I will
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,have prepared the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're just talking about using calibrated levels of consciousness to make it a more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,effective world, a more peaceful world, a more gratifying world for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get anything out of the fact that some country became, what do you call it, a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,world that's not just for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call it in America?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it do anything for me that these people here bought democracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I care if they bought democracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should these people even care about these people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they have a commonality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've got to find where is the commonality that we can talk in a meaningful way to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And hopefully, that would make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That would make diplomatic relationships beneficial and increase the likelihood of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,peace except war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So we tend to increase the power of the field through truth and diminish its destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,by falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after that, we'll conclude quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after that, we'll do questions and answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to move through our questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go through a lot of questions and answers, sign books, and we have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,out of here at 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a crocodile under your chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they're hearing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a crocodile slowly coming down the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you hear me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have plenty of time for questions and answers and signing books, and we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to be out of here by 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a wedding right after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll be responsible and considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And only hedge on their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only hedge on their time a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So let us proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we tried to cover the important things during the lecture and bring it into today's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,world because people tend to compartmentalize spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the old style, Sunday morning, and then the rest of the week, you do what you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've tried to bring spiritual reality into today's headlines, today's news, its reality
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as it impacts our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:13:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our life here in this world, and how to see things beyond just perception, how to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the core, the energy out of which they are coming, and instead of being manipulated by
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,rhetoric.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So are we ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got somebody, people with questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Resume break at 3.15.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll limit your question to one, please, because you see how many other people are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on a limited time schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you have any questions, we'll be happy to answer them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you could please limit your question to one, we would appreciate it.
