Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We all did Est, it was terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I liked about it is, the basic thing was taking responsibility and disqualifying
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,excuses and blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you got there late, you said, I was late because the traffic held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and then they say, and what is the truth of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you're late because you're late if you're responsible you would have left early so in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,case you ran into a traffic jam you would have been here on time so the s would make you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,outside the door until you got honest and admitted the only one that decided to be here late is you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't weasel out of it so s was designed to take you over calibration level 200
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh i think it did a great job of that thank you yeah these are my books took people into
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity beyond 200 stop blaming others you see blame blame projecting responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,instantly throws you below 200 and all the weak losers in the world uh feel sorry for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves and blame everything around them and by doing that they can lower their calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,their power so they don't attract to them that which is successful so the way to success is to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,be honest and integrity and accept the responsibility for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in your environment if a coffee pot falls off the shelf i look within myself to see what is careless
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,i don't blame the coffee pot i always assume responsibility for everything that happens in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,my life or in my environment and you know i've calibrated the energy field just about everything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe and picked up some discordant energies and had to cure them in myself you know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you tried to clear something there and it was a energy of discord and the way i picked it up is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,i got a new fax machine and it was screwing up all the time so instead of saying well it's the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,manufacturer of the fax machine there must be something in me that's pulling that into my field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then i went back i saw where i picked it up cleared it in myself that my reality is the harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the oneness cohesiveness of god and i'm not subject to discord see that's so that really
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,comes s was the first promoter of that degree of integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah so we're all grateful to warner for that thank you yep my coach prods me when i get out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of line she's good isn't she and i take responsibility for that i'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,i try to over explain things because i want to make sure people get it so it comes out of years
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of being a therapist or a psychoanalyst to explain it to make sure that they are getting it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and i still tend to do it yeah boy am i
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in the right seat yeah will you help contextualize for me subjectivity objectivity and where is the
