Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you know you're asking me a question yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but within the class that's the subject of reality okay which is independent of content
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever question you ask me you're still going to get the feeling of of me being the source and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencer of it you know that's the radically subjective yeah is the absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the radically subjective is the field of the absolute the presence within yourself the self
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with the capital s is the radical source of one's own existence beyond all content
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,people take existence for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to look to where the knowingness of existence is arising, that leads you to the very base
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself, takes you out of content, takes you to context, and that's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to the realization of reality, non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then objectivity would be duality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, objectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can be meant in several ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:19:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I was using it in the lecture today was res cogitans, that's your experience
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of your mentalization, and then there's the world the way it is, totally independent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of your existence or your opinion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what in scientific thinking the Newtonian paradigm is called objectivity, the world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it is, not what you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you would have to have a position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To be objective, to be in objectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because it doesn't need anybody to comment about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is without you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you say it's absolute, that's your thinkingness, no you just thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha, aha, yeah, I need some more work on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:20:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little abstract when you talk about it theoretically, but you know the subjective
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,world in which you live, and the world the way it is, sometimes is in accord and quite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,often is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a very rich background in spiritual matters, but I've had a lot of experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot of them have to do with chakras opening and convincing me the reality of chakras
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, I just had a haircut a little while ago and it was about the worst experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It just felt like someone was cutting through a field over and over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was really uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something I should be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I never get them, that's for the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A home haircut's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you get your ear poked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I have, like, some pressure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all kind of overwhelming because it's been pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would do the Thymic Thump right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do the Thymic Thump.
