Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now your acupuncture is better balanced, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be all right.
