Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, will this feel like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This just feels like there's a cord or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, I don't like talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle of March, I was meditating and had an experience, sort of,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,where the top of my head no longer felt like the top of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Beard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a topless fella?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this is why I don't like talking about it, Dr. Hawkins.
