Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no, it felt like instead of what it had been,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it kind of folded in on itself and there was something.
