Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it was, but it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your experience of your body image, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, just walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What I find is like, I don't know, I feel, sometimes I feel clumsy because I'm not exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,sure where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I feel like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you done any energy chakra balancing or acupuncture?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, see, I don't know anything about that because I'm just really naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you said you had a number of experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, I have had the experiences, but I don't know what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you need a spiritual teacher, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't find anybody because I've gone around to people in Boston and they don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they kind of look at me like, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what kind of teachers are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I went to a Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a Shambhala center.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to more traditional Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not the place to go, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think it's more energy balancing kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I would look at your chakra system and polarity therapy.
