Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Reiki, what do the people do with your feet kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflexology.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflexology.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I would look into energy medicine, energy medicine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then see if that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't work, it should, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this, will this persist, the feeling of being in the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't foretell the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.94,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I would just do what the doctor says.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for energy medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for energy medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out first there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a complicated problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take some study.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take some diagnostic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take some energy work to see what chakras and what energy is out.
