Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have picked it up from the barber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say thank you to you.
