Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty much all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I did have a question about prayer, but you answered it earlier about raising the.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.13,0:24:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my name I wrote in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.25,0:24:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too legible, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my scrawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.21,0:24:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I sort of am in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.13,0:24:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My question was about cause, and you also totally and completely answered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.23,0:24:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel real comfortable with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I just also want to thank you for the blessing that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.95,0:24:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.23,0:24:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also want a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.06,0:24:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you also want a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.67,0:24:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to be a dollar now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.06,0:24:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.91,0:25:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, honey, for what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.72,0:25:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.77,0:25:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.97,0:25:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.54,0:25:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.58,0:25:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you so much for teaching and writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.95,0:25:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.58,0:25:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a blessing to me and so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.10,0:25:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them here and elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you about a spiritual experience I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.28,0:25:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And for you to comment on it, kind of tell me where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I woke up one morning, and I was wide awake, and I rolled over and hugged my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.99,0:25:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt love for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.08,0:25:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden, I was somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.13,0:25:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't really describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.17,0:26:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.04,0:26:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody told me what did it look like, I'd have to say light.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.65,0:26:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was just in a place where I felt great power, and it was very peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.99,0:26:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.93,0:26:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.61,0:26:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I look like I was complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.96,0:26:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You went into a great space.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.38,0:26:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I went into this great space.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.05,0:26:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.25,0:26:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other thing I noticed about it was that even though it was totally alien to my experience here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.48,0:26:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the wrong word.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.09,0:26:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, totally different from anything that we could experience here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.44,0:26:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,More advanced than what you're used to, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.07,0:26:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't know whether it was advanced or not, but it was totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.55,0:26:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was light and love?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.35,0:26:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.70,0:26:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.81,0:26:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt very familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.79,0:26:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt extremely familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.22,0:27:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.46,0:27:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of recognized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.81,0:27:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.85,0:27:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Recognition, yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.07,0:27:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it was very comfortable and familiar, and it wasn't bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.48,0:27:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.79,0:27:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.31,0:27:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.85,0:27:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.75,0:27:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't feel this enormous love that I hear some people talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.57,0:27:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.80,0:27:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.32,0:27:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where did I go, and what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.06,0:27:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you just went into a more advanced state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.24,0:27:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The characteristics of near-death experience, out-of-body experiences, that are varied from individual to individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.11,0:27:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You may experience just the presence of love with no light, or you may experience just light and clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.64,0:27:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because divinity has various characteristics of light, love, oneness, balance, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.23,0:27:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.84,0:27:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.89,0:27:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You may experience the presence of God as suddenly overwhelmed by the stunning beauty of your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.54,0:27:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can walk through the woods and suddenly almost pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.21,0:28:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the incredible beauty, like, shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.15,0:28:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's divinity expressing itself through your awareness as beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.11,0:28:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you may get it as infinite silence, infinite love, infinite light.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.81,0:28:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.25,0:28:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.83,0:28:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.99,0:28:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I could say I experienced it as infinite power and silence and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.15,0:28:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.30,0:28:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And a feeling of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.10,0:28:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, familiarity is part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.56,0:28:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What you was at was, you knew that you was over 500, 540, 540, 35, 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.74,0:28:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You was about 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.22,0:28:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you start having those experiences, you get more advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.50,0:28:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings of oneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.83,0:28:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling as though suddenly everything is silent, and you're living in a mystical world of the endlessly miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.67,0:28:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt very miraculous, and it was short, but I was definitely there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.63,0:29:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I just sort of, I was overwhelmed with the wonder of it, and I gasped, and that closed the door for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.43,0:29:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.93,0:29:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's transitory in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.58,0:29:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.34,0:29:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.84,0:29:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's transitory because you're above your karma, and then the karma catches up with you again, and they disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.73,0:29:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you keep going, doing spiritual work, and you rise above your karma, and you have wonderful experiences, and then the karma sort of catches up with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.20,0:29:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.41,0:29:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the beginning, they tend to be evanescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.69,0:29:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the spiritual Christian saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.47,0:29:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, why hast thou forsaken me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.73,0:29:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, lover, why hast thou left me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.73,0:29:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware that wailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.36,0:29:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's characteristic of these early experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.54,0:29:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappears, and you feel like you've done something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.08,0:29:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel like you're forsaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.06,0:29:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it's idiotic, but you go back to the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.36,0:29:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the same park, in the same corner where it happened, and of course, it doesn't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.36,0:29:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it's ridiculous even when you do it, but still, somehow, it's like trying to recapture that experience, because they're transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.76,0:30:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.47,0:30:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about spiritual work that people don't quite get, and it has to be emphasized, is perseverance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.47,0:30:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I think in the Course in Miracles it's called faithfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.47,0:30:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Perseverance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.50,0:30:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you don't do it for five minutes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.00,0:30:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then go to the ball game, and then tomorrow at noon you suddenly remember to do it for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.50,0:30:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Saturday you think, oh, I'll meditate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.50,0:30:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.50,0:30:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's sort of sporadic, interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.50,0:30:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is you get a fixity of intention, a continuousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.14,0:30:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to let go of things as they arise, and you're serious about it, you do it continuously, continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.75,0:30:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be aware of the field instead of the content of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.25,0:30:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.25,0:31:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see life as a presence, and everything happening as a consequence of the presence, you do that continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.20,0:31:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was one thing I was going to talk about today, and I'm glad you mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.31,0:31:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here, persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.31,0:31:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave myself a note about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.31,0:31:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The persistence of the determination of the process, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.42,0:31:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're forgiving, then you forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just forgive for an hour today, ten minutes tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.22,0:31:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you go into a really advanced state, it's with one pointedness of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.59,0:31:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, certain pathways, what they first do is train you how to attain one pointedness of mind before you even try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.59,0:31:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the tool you're going to need.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.59,0:31:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot deviate one iota.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.59,0:31:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going through surgery without anesthesia, you better walk the edge of the razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.59,0:31:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.99,0:31:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then if you try to hang on to the pain you just experienced, it's agonizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.98,0:32:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience has to be non-resistive, let go of it at the very moment of its crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.98,0:32:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you move along the crest of the moment of now, with the roll call of now, experiential immediacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.57,0:32:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.57,0:32:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.86,0:32:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll come back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.86,0:32:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.86,0:32:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.86,0:32:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.86,0:32:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over explaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.86,0:32:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got pushed and nudged.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.86,0:32:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your book?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.64,0:32:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.64,0:32:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.27,0:32:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.27,0:32:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have someone peeing off the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.27,0:32:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.27,0:32:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.27,0:32:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.27,0:32:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.17,0:32:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a lot of people have those early transitory experiences, and it worries them that they've disappeared or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.17,0:32:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.17,0:32:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.17,0:32:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would gladly pay you Tuesday if I could only have a hug today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.17,0:32:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gives me a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.17,0:32:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.17,0:32:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you where I got that in the mountains of Peru, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.17,0:32:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.35,0:33:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And actually, I'll add 10 to my credit if I can get a jig.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.35,0:33:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.35,0:33:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A jig.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.35,0:33:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A jig.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.35,0:33:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.35,0:33:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I haven't got the energy for a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.51,0:33:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For $10.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.51,0:33:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.51,0:33:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.51,0:33:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.51,0:33:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.72,0:33:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.72,0:33:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.72,0:33:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.72,0:33:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.72,0:33:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.64,0:33:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.64,0:33:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.24,0:33:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.24,0:33:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.50,0:33:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.50,0:33:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.50,0:33:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.40,0:33:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.40,0:33:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.40,0:33:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.40,0:33:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.88,0:33:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.98,0:33:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.98,0:33:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.98,0:33:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.98,0:33:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.98,0:33:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
