Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.98,0:34:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.98,0:34:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.98,0:34:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.98,0:34:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.98,0:34:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.98,0:34:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.98,0:34:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.98,0:34:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.98,0:34:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.98,0:34:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.98,0:34:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.98,0:34:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.98,0:34:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more important for me whether one should really choose one path
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.11,0:34:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether they can use both avatars.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.98,0:34:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two different things. No, not two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.63,0:34:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the same thing, but in a different context.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.09,0:34:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ was born, and he never had a previous human lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.01,0:34:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His purpose is salvation, somewhat like the representation of Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.17,0:34:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as Avalokiteshvara, the Buddha of infinite mercy, of lowest land Buddhism.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.80,0:34:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What Christ says is, strive for unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.36,0:35:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do so in my name, I will be your spokesman in the celestial realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.86,0:35:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which in this world is called heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.67,0:35:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha never had any previous lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.48,0:35:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry. The Buddha had many previous lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.57,0:35:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Represents enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.61,0:35:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is a different ultimate objective from salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.76,0:35:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha's enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is also realistic, that the likelihood of reaching enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.19,0:35:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime is extremely small.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.32,0:35:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you live as good a life as you can, and by karmic merit,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.15,0:35:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you will land in the lotus land, which is a celestial realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.09,0:35:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the Buddha of the celestial realm will be your advocate,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.48,0:35:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as Christ is in Christian heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.34,0:35:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the rest of the thing to do is be a Buddhist Christian or a Christian Buddhist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.73,0:36:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.88,0:36:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The only difference is ecclesiastic doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.07,0:36:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the teaching of Jesus Christ,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.21,0:36:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's the ecclesiastic doctrine of some church.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.19,0:36:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher is the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.86,0:36:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The church is the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.67,0:36:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often, people don't get into spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.44,0:36:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They get into religionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.94,0:36:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.96,0:36:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap of religionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.82,0:36:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What you wear, whether you shave or don't shave,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.00,0:36:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what you eat, sex, no, sex is all irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.88,0:36:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And they get caught up in all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.30,0:36:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you call me here on the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.53,0:36:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The right side is all irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.38,0:36:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.88,0:36:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.98,0:36:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already got the core of it, or you wouldn't be asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.96,0:36:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.30,0:36:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Greed for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.09,0:36:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.73,0:36:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.42,0:36:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.73,0:37:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, honey. I'll keep that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.03,0:37:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it in my memory book.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.03,0:37:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.03,0:37:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.53,0:37:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would give me a die, I'd put them away for my old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.17,0:37:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save them for my old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.28,0:37:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to eat them then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.28,0:37:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.82,0:37:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, does some food calibrate below 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.82,0:37:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And does it really matter what you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.82,0:37:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Food in general, generically, calibrates around 200 or 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.82,0:37:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've got to move over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.82,0:37:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate 200, 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.82,0:37:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Food calibrates at 200, 202.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.82,0:37:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,200.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.82,0:37:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.82,0:37:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The food in general, generically, calibrates around 200 or 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.82,0:37:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've got to move over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.82,0:37:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate 200, 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.82,0:37:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Food calibrates at 200, 202.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.82,0:37:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,200.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.82,0:37:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.82,0:37:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When you bless food, it jumps to 207, 208.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.82,0:37:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When you bless food, it automatically energizes, raises the energy of the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.21,0:37:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it is food that calibrates below 200, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.21,0:37:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never eaten at a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.21,0:37:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.21,0:37:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.21,0:37:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.92,0:37:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.92,0:37:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.92,0:37:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.92,0:37:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.92,0:37:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.13,0:37:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.13,0:37:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.13,0:37:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.13,0:37:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,eating at a restaurant. There is? Yeah, remember, it's that dead food. Oh yeah, dead food, yes. Oh yes, you're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.67,0:38:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine-made food calibrates below 200. You can tell it. It's like it's dead when you put it in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.34,0:38:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,your mouth. Food that's manufactured with human intervention, even if it's somebody overseeing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.69,0:38:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the pot where it's cooking, it raises the energy level above 200. Okay, so don't eat dad's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.59,0:38:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't say don't eat it. Bless it. Okay. I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.09,0:38:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's cat food that calibrates below 200. My cat won't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.42,0:38:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I bless it for her. Okay, thank you. No, there's really brands of cat food that calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.67,0:38:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200, and there's one brand, Big Cellar, calibrates below 200. You know, my cat will not
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.40,0:38:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,eat it. She just sits there and looks at it. Well, looks at it, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.40,0:38:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you better calibrate your kitty's food, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.71,0:39:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any questions, because you've answered at least them for today. So I just
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.15,0:39:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to say thank you for your materials and your presence. Yes. This has really added to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.53,0:39:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,my evolution. Good, thank you so much. Thank you. What color eyes are those? What color are you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,calling them? Huh? You've got pretty eyes. That's a sort of a greenish-brownish, mysterious look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.28,0:39:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hazel. Hazel. I think they call them hazel eyes. Hazel. Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.07,0:39:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.67,0:39:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If the idea of enlightenment is a goal for this lifetime, what is a very effective practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.92,0:39:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were listening during the lecture today? Yes. I know, but we have different guides teach
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.00,0:39:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,different ideas. I don't know if you've heard of it. I don't know if you've heard of it. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.69,0:40:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the different forms of meditation and different topics of meditation?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.50,0:40:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the only formal meditation I've ever done is Zen style, Zen. You go to a Zen monastery,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.90,0:40:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you go to a Zen monk, go to a Zen organization, and that's what I would do. Do the world's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.07,0:40:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said that the time of death is predestined for this lifetime. Is the ability
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.63,0:40:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to attain enlightenment also? No. No. Okay. Thank you. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.82,0:40:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The law of the universe is freedom. Every instant you're free to choose a this or a that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.73,0:40:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a this or a that, until you see there's no more of this or that, and then it stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.71,0:40:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Yeah. I would look up a Zen. It's facilitated by will, yeah, but it comes on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.46,0:41:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,on its own, yeah. One once said that the final doorway isn't far away for anybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.80,0:41:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that? You, actually. No, I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.71,0:41:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know? It depends on what you mean by far away. Well, you know, a hundred lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.90,0:41:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is short, close by, yes. Right, right. Yeah, just, I guess I'm speaking from a dualistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.63,0:41:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,unenlightened point of view. So, like, even the depths of despair, something could happen
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.30,0:41:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,where, boom, you know. Oh, yes. Or, but in a progression where somebody is dedicated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.88,0:41:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to devotional non-dwelling. You don't know when and how it's going to happen. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.34,0:41:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's not a linear phenomenon. Right. At the most unexpected moment, there's not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.11,0:41:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a linear phenomenon. Right. There's not a linear phenomenon. There's not a linear phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.32,0:41:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, there you have it. Yeah. That's why I like people to have the information
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.44,0:41:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in advance, because you come into a sudden realization. At that point, there's no memory
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.51,0:42:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of anything. You say, well, I'll remember what I learned. No, you won't. At that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.57,0:42:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the frequency and the vibration of your aura radiates a knowingness, non-verbally. You
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.03,0:42:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,just know to go this way. And the last fear comes up. And the knowingness. And the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.78,0:42:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,said, all fear is illusion. Surrender it to God. So, even in the grip of terror, you walk
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.78,0:42:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,through the door, and it is the ultimate truth. Okay. So, there wouldn't be, if somebody stays
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.78,0:42:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,on a path of devotional non-duality and, say, goes through levels of consciousness, would
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.55,0:42:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they experience certain things prior, possibly? Are there certain experiences that seem common
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.61,0:42:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as somebody who progresses consciously, as opposed to, like, a sudden? No, it's not a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.11,0:42:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,linear progression like that. Right. Okay. It may be. Yeah, I see. It may be period,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.38,0:42:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you feel like you're making great progress for a whole year, let's say. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.07,0:42:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly you feel like you're bogged down. Like, God, I'm meditating, nothing's happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.78,0:42:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting nowhere. Well, you're undoing stacks of karma, see? And as that karmic obligation
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.86,0:43:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,gets dispelled, then you move ahead again, yeah? Okay, cool. Yeah. So, never worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.19,0:43:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Alrighty. Thanks so much. Never look at the mileage meter. Okay. Alrighty. Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.44,0:43:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.71,0:43:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel very blessed. Yeah. Yeah, it's not a linear logical progression. In fact, when
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.11,0:43:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you think you're doing the worst, you can suddenly make a leap, and when you think you're
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.13,0:43:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,doing great, you can suddenly crash. So, yeah. Okay. Yeah, go ahead. One question. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.23,0:43:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother watch is over, so don't worry about it. Okay. Bottom of the context is I'm a third
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.34,0:43:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,grade teacher, okay? Okay. So, can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.05,0:43:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a third grade teacher. Okay. So, can I become better at... So, can I recontextualize
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.61,0:44:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the learning of my students who are eight and nine-year-olds to move them to a level
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.46,0:44:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness such that I can teach them how to do kinesiology so that they can walk
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.11,0:44:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,out the door... At age nine? At age eight and nine. I don't know that you can actually
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.03,0:44:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,teach it. I've demonstrated it on videotape, you know, using kids. Kids are very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.92,0:44:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can teach them how to do that. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.59,0:44:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even have to know anything. They just hold this picture over your tummy, now
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.48,0:44:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,resist. Hitler makes them go weak, Lincoln makes them go strong. We've done that a hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.42,0:44:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,times. So, as long as you don't have objection from the community or the parents that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.28,0:44:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching something esoteric, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.01,0:44:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't enough like Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.51,0:44:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't want you to have to drink hemlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.71,0:44:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hemlock and soda, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.71,0:44:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was Socrates, I'd say, how about Virginia Jarrell, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.21,0:44:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only death anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.05,0:44:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.17,0:45:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, we have a demonstration video we did back in 95. Early videos, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.73,0:45:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I did them off in the ranch there. And they were very informal, but honest, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.88,0:45:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But not a Hollywood production. But, you know, we demonstrated many things with innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.44,0:45:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,people, you know? An innocent child doesn't know what that is. And we were showing the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.73,0:45:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,disparity between perception and belief and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.44,0:45:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, things that the world thinks will make you go weak didn't make her go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.44,0:45:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Things they thought, the world thought would make her go strong, she went weak. So, we
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.48,0:45:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,just used her as an indicator of, uh, pretty reliable. Kids make very good test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.13,0:45:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.13,0:45:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta pay them a dollar every time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.67,0:46:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had one question that I was going to ask you, which I think you've already answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.86,0:46:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a young friend, Sage, who...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.36,0:46:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who was with Eckhart Tolle, uh, up in Canada. And, uh, she had this enlightening experience
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.50,0:46:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and was out teaching, and then has lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.00,0:46:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.00,0:46:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think you answered that, that that's not that unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.50,0:46:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's common.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.03,0:46:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And, and I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.03,0:46:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's almost, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.53,0:46:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.53,0:46:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember, this got out of Maharaj, says the thing, I think, or Ramana Maharshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.53,0:46:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget. A couple of those teachers in the 700s said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.53,0:46:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.53,0:46:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That it comes and goes, and, uh, then you, it's like you rise above your karma, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.53,0:46:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you go back and, and undo some more karma, and then you seem, you think you've lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.53,0:46:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.53,0:47:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the illumination, it's a revelation of what's to come. So, one should be encouraged
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.53,0:47:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by the fact they had it all, instead of discouraged that it's not continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.53,0:47:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then just persevere through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.53,0:47:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.53,0:47:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I had a good opportunity, I saw Nisargadatta in 1976.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.53,0:47:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.53,0:47:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh, spent about two and a half years there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.53,0:47:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was a real privilege, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.53,0:47:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.53,0:47:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.53,0:47:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.53,0:47:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.53,0:47:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, when I was reading your introduction last week, someone gave me a book up in Calgary,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.53,0:47:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and, uh, how I discovered you were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.53,0:47:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.53,0:47:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And very much appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.53,0:47:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.53,0:47:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you, when are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.53,0:47:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in Toronto next weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.53,0:47:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.53,0:47:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're going to Toronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.53,0:47:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.53,0:47:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the, sort of, the west, west side.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.53,0:47:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.53,0:47:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't gone to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.53,0:47:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.55,0:47:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll get up to Calgary if we, uh, invite you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.55,0:47:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.55,0:47:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.55,0:47:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.55,0:47:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.55,0:47:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.55,0:47:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.59,0:47:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.59,0:47:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.59,0:47:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.59,0:47:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.59,0:47:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.59,0:47:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Calgary's right north of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.59,0:47:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.59,0:47:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.59,0:47:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad trip up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.59,0:47:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been to Calgary in a lot of years, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.59,0:47:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.59,0:47:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.59,0:47:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very nice, uh, high energy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.59,0:47:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That I was once there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.59,0:47:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.59,0:47:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.59,0:47:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.59,0:48:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question for myself, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.59,0:48:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How, how do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.59,0:48:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.59,0:48:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.59,0:48:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And to everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.59,0:48:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we establish the, um, conscious, uh, uh, level that we're at?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.59,0:48:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To, if we're going to go and do, uh, some, uh, uh, muscle testing and question with somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.59,0:48:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,else.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.59,0:48:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.59,0:48:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean we're above 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.98,0:48:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.98,0:48:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,People below 200 are not interested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.98,0:48:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.98,0:48:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.98,0:48:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be at this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.98,0:48:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.98,0:48:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.98,0:48:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.98,0:48:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't have sat through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.98,0:48:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.98,0:48:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.98,0:48:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.98,0:48:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had people below 200 wander into the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.98,0:48:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And they usually will get up indignantly and stomp out somewhere in the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.98,0:48:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.98,0:48:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.98,0:48:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.98,0:48:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If nobody got outraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.98,0:48:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.98,0:48:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And didn't stomp out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.98,0:48:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they weren't below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.98,0:48:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.98,0:48:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.98,0:48:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.98,0:48:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.98,0:48:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.98,0:48:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.98,0:48:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of establish ourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.98,0:48:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.98,0:48:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.98,0:48:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.98,0:48:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.26,0:48:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.26,0:48:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of chart our progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.26,0:48:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact we're.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.26,0:48:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to chart it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.26,0:48:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.26,0:49:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.26,0:49:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.26,0:49:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.26,0:49:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.26,0:49:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.26,0:49:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You got nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.26,0:49:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.26,0:49:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,God's retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.26,0:49:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He just sits up there and gets advice from all those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.26,0:49:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.26,0:49:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.26,0:49:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Listens to complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.26,0:49:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.32,0:49:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys they answer the email.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.32,0:49:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.32,0:49:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.61,0:49:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.61,0:49:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a hug too?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.61,0:49:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.80,0:49:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.80,0:49:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You knocked my microphone right off my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.80,0:49:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.80,0:49:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.80,0:49:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I stuck it in my eye one time on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.80,0:49:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you get this freaking thing back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.32,0:49:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here let me get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.32,0:49:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.32,0:49:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.32,0:49:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I knocked it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.32,0:49:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.42,0:49:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.42,0:49:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.42,0:49:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.42,0:49:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a bird man from some planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.42,0:49:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Distant planet or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.42,0:49:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll look forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.42,0:49:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.42,0:49:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.42,0:49:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.42,0:49:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.42,0:49:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.42,0:49:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.42,0:49:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.42,0:49:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.42,0:49:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.42,0:49:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.42,0:49:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.42,0:49:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.42,0:49:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed so strange when we first got it but person who sold me on it was the Unity
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.69,0:49:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.69,0:49:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She says, once you get used to it, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.67,0:50:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats anything going.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.30,0:50:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.30,0:50:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've worn it for a while, you don't know it's there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.01,0:50:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.05,0:50:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thank you first of all for today and for your books that I've read.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.07,0:50:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband and I feel we're on a spiritual path.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.94,0:50:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We moved from Atlanta, Georgia, to a small town in Georgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.05,0:50:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're moving to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.80,0:50:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We felt compelled to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.86,0:50:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And does place matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.34,0:50:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Does place matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.90,0:50:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.63,0:50:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.92,0:50:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what's within that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.88,0:50:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's more as you move ahead, you look for what would,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.36,0:50:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that was just more concordant with where you are within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.13,0:50:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.63,0:50:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When I moved out here, as I say, I didn't have a refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.90,0:50:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't take the noise of it, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.42,0:50:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.38,0:51:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted stillness, peace, and there was nobody in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.36,0:51:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They closed it up all winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.55,0:51:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one restaurant open, and it closed at 8 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.88,0:51:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much smaller than it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.84,0:51:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was just fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.23,0:51:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it seems like a thriving metropolis,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.86,0:51:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I avoid Sedona and get out of town as quick as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.38,0:51:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On downsizing, we're having to decide what to bring,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.80,0:51:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because the place here is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.65,0:51:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.51,0:51:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I, how does one have the confidence in kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.59,0:51:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're going through your big book collection
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.36,0:51:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to know which ones to come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.07,0:51:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.94,0:51:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people that are good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.57,0:51:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have confidence in yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.19,0:51:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't have confidence in your own capacity,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.71,0:51:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there's people who are good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.71,0:51:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask them to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.73,0:51:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.82,0:51:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.42,0:52:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,May I also have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.65,0:52:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as spiritual libraries,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.21,0:52:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thrown them out two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.94,0:52:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.98,0:52:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.65,0:52:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.15,0:52:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.98,0:52:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I left 6,000 volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.15,0:52:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I, in Sedona, began stacking them up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.46,0:52:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I left all of them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.38,0:52:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And now to write this book, I've got to collect them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.76,0:52:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how many copies of the Rig Vita do you have to buy in a lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.46,0:52:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.76,0:52:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have mixed emotions of being up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.11,0:52:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The last two people that came up did not have to give you a dollar for a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.00,0:52:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one was a male.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.78,0:52:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All the rest of the women you asked, so what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.07,0:52:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, hugs are for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.84,0:52:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hugs are for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.48,0:52:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hugs are for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.28,0:52:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.94,0:53:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendly hugs cost a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.34,0:53:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.34,0:53:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's a mesomorph.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.69,0:53:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.13,0:53:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a mesomorph.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.21,0:53:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a mesomorph.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.28,0:53:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a mesomorph.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.30,0:53:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a mesomorph.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.32,0:53:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was prepared to pay two, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.61,0:53:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, one dollar is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.36,0:53:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it in my piggy bank for when I get old.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.48,0:53:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We are a group of 22 men here on a spiritual path.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.69,0:53:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the things that we do is we hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.94,0:53:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.13,0:53:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's one of the reasons that...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.19,0:53:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.61,0:53:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To get in touch with both our feminine and masculine...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.55,0:53:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll give you a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.07,0:53:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.92,0:53:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.65,0:53:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll get to my...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.48,0:53:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.19,0:53:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.01,0:53:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here again, as everybody else has said, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.53,0:53:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I've had some insight, and this has to do with a relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.94,0:54:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in a personal relationship with an immediate family.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.46,0:54:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the things that I've struggled with for quite some time is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.63,0:54:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see somebody that you love in the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.90,0:54:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are some demonstrations of things that...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.36,0:54:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,behaviors that you do not go along with,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.09,0:54:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're afraid to confront them with it because of your relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.76,0:54:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what is my responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.96,0:54:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is my responsibility in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.88,0:54:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.67,0:54:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a thing of overcoming, how do I overcome that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.13,0:54:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's touchy very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.78,0:54:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12-step groups work on that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.28,0:54:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Al-Anon and all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.19,0:54:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether to say nothing, you're being an enabler,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.15,0:54:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether to say something, you're trying to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.09,0:54:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you screw it either way, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.46,0:54:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.63,0:54:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.28,0:54:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.59,0:54:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to be that which would make a mirror back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.48,0:54:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.28,0:55:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same time, use spiritual techniques such as prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.11,0:55:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You pray for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.57,0:55:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you do the course of miracles and ask for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.96,0:55:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you've done all you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.40,0:55:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.84,0:55:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.61,0:55:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that don't work, you tell him he either straightens up
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.96,0:55:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or he gets his ass the hell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.67,0:55:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know I'm touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.86,0:55:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.15,0:55:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I want to say thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.46,0:55:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your books have had such a positive impact on my life
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.26,0:55:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's just been incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.19,0:55:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just grateful for your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.01,0:55:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.28,0:55:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the chance that I got to come and see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.51,0:55:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And second of all, my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.86,0:56:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've wondered this in childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.82,0:56:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,how many licks does it take to get to the center
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.94,0:56:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of a tattoo roll lollipop?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.59,0:56:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it a whirly mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.23,0:56:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the more it spins and then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.32,0:56:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.51,0:56:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's written all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.34,0:56:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that disrespectful?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.78,0:56:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.78,0:56:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.61,0:56:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Canada and just came to say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.26,0:56:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.92,0:56:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got so many Canadians lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.78,0:57:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.46,0:57:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to get above 415.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.46,0:57:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're going to be in Toronto next weekend, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.98,0:57:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.38,0:57:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Help our brothers, our brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.44,0:57:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Dennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.32,0:57:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.44,0:57:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.67,0:57:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.98,0:57:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.09,0:58:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't been in Canada in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.57,0:58:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.17,0:58:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to fly there once a month from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.09,0:58:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.90,0:58:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the board of directors of Weber Pharmaceuticals.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.46,0:58:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Weber, W-B-E-R.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.80,0:58:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They manufactured vitamin E,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.53,0:58:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and we were interested in researching the effect of vitamin E,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.59,0:58:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,which is an antioxidant, on longevity, cardiac disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.32,0:58:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and improving mental disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.38,0:58:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By improving the environment of the mind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.32,0:58:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I used to go there once a month, fly up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.57,0:58:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.65,0:58:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you're in Canada because everything's suddenly sane and neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.84,0:58:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,On this side, everything looks chaotic and rubbishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.38,0:58:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get on the Canadian side, and here's this stunning apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.82,0:58:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a whole city block, all lawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.65,0:58:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle is this apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.76,0:58:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you park underneath the apartment building,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.05,0:58:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so the streets are not all littered with cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.94,0:58:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.05,0:58:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that, to me, is Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.38,0:58:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.55,0:59:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And this side, it was cars parked this way, and this way, and this way, and chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.65,0:59:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my idea, memory of Canada is pristine and can be in the beauty of pristine clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.17,0:59:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, it had a beautiful green lawn, and the cars are parked under the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.36,0:59:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't see them all around, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.80,0:59:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my memory of Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.92,0:59:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.40,0:59:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the way it is, or is that my dream state?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.34,0:59:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.69,0:59:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.94,0:59:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.67,0:59:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as an old-time obsessive-compulsive, it makes me real happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.01,0:59:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aloha.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.82,0:59:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.88,0:59:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Which island?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.09,0:59:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kauai.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.69,0:59:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aloha and mahalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.30,0:59:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a quick question on walk-ins, question mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.19,0:59:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.03,0:59:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.57,0:59:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a truth as walk-ins?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.38,0:59:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.19,0:59:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.07,0:59:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.55,0:59:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a reality result.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.48,1:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual belief system, it's an actual reality result.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.36,1:00:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a belief system, that clears that up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.42,1:00:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been asked that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.98,1:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that we ever did it, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.75,1:00:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was way back in the beginning, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.34,1:00:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.34,1:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we did it at home, I think, one time, but I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.75,1:00:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good to know, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.09,1:00:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.09,1:00:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we got the same one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.09,1:00:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.11,1:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct, we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.11,1:00:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We got about 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.11,1:00:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have come to Kauai.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.11,1:00:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've been asked to come to Kauai.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.11,1:00:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have come to Kauai.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.11,1:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been asked to come to Kauai about three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.11,1:00:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.11,1:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't confirmed anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.11,1:00:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we will be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.11,1:00:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.11,1:00:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I need a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.23,1:00:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.23,1:00:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back to Kauai without one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.32,1:00:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.32,1:00:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.32,1:00:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I was in Hawaii was 1945.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.32,1:00:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The war was over, and we came back through Pearl Harbor, through, what the hell was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.32,1:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it there?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.32,1:00:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.32,1:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Point or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.32,1:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.32,1:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.76,1:00:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.76,1:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.76,1:00:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.76,1:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.28,1:00:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.28,1:00:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.28,1:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.53,1:01:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.53,1:01:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.21,1:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.21,1:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.21,1:01:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.21,1:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.21,1:01:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.30,1:01:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.30,1:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We went out through Diamond Head, and those of us that made it back came back through
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.30,1:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.30,1:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.30,1:01:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.32,1:01:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We come to the classes and it feels like we get a real lift, and then we get home Monday
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.75,1:01:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,morning and it seems to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.23,1:01:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You go back to work and you get buried back in work.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.01,1:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about recontact.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.84,1:01:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.84,1:01:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,textualizing in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.32,1:01:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you speak to that,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.17,1:01:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how one can retextualize and not fall into that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.57,1:01:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.11,1:01:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you give everything you do your maximum,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.94,1:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and you surrender it to God as you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.86,1:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you bring up the joy of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.59,1:02:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At this moment, I'm answering you to the best I can,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.82,1:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm very conscious and aware of your presence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.55,1:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the presence of the books and the presence of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.61,1:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being maximally what I can be at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.15,1:02:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no regret that I'm not being more than what I'm being
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.65,1:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm being all that I can be right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.11,1:02:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I dig a ditch, I dig it with absolute ferocity.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.90,1:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that ditch really gets it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.61,1:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I give maximum what I am to everything I do,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.78,1:02:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's more...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.59,1:02:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mowing the lawn, petting the kitty,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.61,1:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.86,1:02:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're writing a book,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.98,1:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you knock your brains out to do the maximum
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.05,1:02:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to actualize your potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.78,1:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And that brings you joy,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.15,1:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so that every moment is equally joyful
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.01,1:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because every moment is equally your maximum
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.17,1:03:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,being the potential of that which you can be every moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.55,1:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm a protester, I'm going to protest to the maximum.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.38,1:03:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be content,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.71,1:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sit there and eat donuts to the maximum.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.23,1:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.67,1:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do whatever I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.57,1:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those donuts?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.13,1:03:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those donuts?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.07,1:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You eat one and you can't have another?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.69,1:03:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.61,1:03:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.61,1:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I stay out of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.19,1:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Krusty something, rather?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.63,1:03:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I stay out of those places.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.07,1:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They bring them into my office.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.69,1:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, I'd say take them away.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.71,1:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.26,1:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Either bring me six or don't bring me any.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.00,1:03:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I purposely never eat in the Krusty
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.80,1:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because I know what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.15,1:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You get buried.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.30,1:03:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you do everything you can do to the maximum.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.92,1:03:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To the maximum.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.15,1:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the source of joy is within you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.86,1:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when you fulfill your potential every minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.09,1:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When you are what you can possibly be
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.86,1:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,from second to second,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.44,1:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.00,1:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of the ditch I dug by hand,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.38,1:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, a long one, big one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.34,1:04:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I think of it now,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.80,1:04:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the best I could on that ditch.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.01,1:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.15,1:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My damn brain valve.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.17,1:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or an ectomorph.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.05,1:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was tough work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.69,1:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.69,1:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.26,1:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.36,1:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.55,1:04:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what you want to do
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.38,1:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is be the best you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.05,1:04:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the best parent you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.30,1:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the best spouse you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.46,1:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the best citizen you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.88,1:04:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the best spiritual example you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.67,1:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're doing all that simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.15,1:04:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.42,1:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't bring you joy,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.94,1:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you a script.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.96,1:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.48,1:04:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.50,1:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.69,1:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's really all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.01,1:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm making a mint today.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.76,1:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to go hungry tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.61,1:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.32,1:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to just be the absolute,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.78,1:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all that you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.36,1:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Every moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.11,1:05:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Every moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.71,1:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, every moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.63,1:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Without relapse.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.03,1:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.46,1:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.59,1:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you pass out as unconscious as you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.71,1:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have someone who hasn't picked up the car keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.13,1:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.53,1:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.65,1:05:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have four.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.88,1:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a truck key up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.94,1:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's lost one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.28,1:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.05,1:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.17,1:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was first going nuts,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.67,1:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some spiritual experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.86,1:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering how much of that was like,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.51,1:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I believe some of the experiences were real,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.96,1:05:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's sort of,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.30,1:05:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,some people with schizophrenia believe that everything they experience was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.55,1:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a great deal of it is pretty messed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.26,1:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm just,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.13,1:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering if the experiences I had were real, or?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.57,1:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they joyful?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.28,1:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Made you happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.63,1:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Connected with infinite oneness?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.17,1:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.32,1:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then they're real.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There were little blue demons dancing around.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.80,1:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably not real.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.01,1:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.73,1:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is always love.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.34,1:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, the presence of love would tell you the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.19,1:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't imitate the presence of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.78,1:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It either is or it is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.65,1:06:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, and such experiences are also described,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.40,1:06:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,described in the kundalini literature.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.90,1:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.09,1:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the kundalini knocking people into temporary psychosis,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.34,1:06:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and Gopi Krishna, I think, mentions it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.25,1:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's others in the kundalini energy,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.26,1:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the energy impacts the brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.50,1:07:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and a person may become sort of out of it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.59,1:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,With prayer and alignment with the truth of God, it cures itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.09,1:07:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I pray, I'll be more likely to get better?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.28,1:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.78,1:07:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.75,1:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you completely and totally surrender to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.57,1:07:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't make any difference whether you recover or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.82,1:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.71,1:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he created you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.96,1:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.92,1:07:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the best you can to straighten your head out, and the rest is up to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.21,1:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.03,1:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.38,1:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.75,1:07:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrender your coverage to God, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.51,1:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, these things are cyclic.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.11,1:07:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You may cycle into it and then cycle out of it, karmic cycles.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.01,1:08:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say, last night I was so excited about coming here today
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.01,1:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that I had a dream you were teaching me how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.84,1:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and you would, like, go under the water,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.51,1:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were teaching me how to, like, hold my breath,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.13,1:08:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was just a great dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.46,1:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I just wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.00,1:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.92,1:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a coach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.03,1:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.44,1:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a swimming coach.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.46,1:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.03,1:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I brought a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.73,1:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God I'm making a mint today.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.53,1:08:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.48,1:08:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.40,1:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's neat, a swimming coach.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.72,1:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.68,1:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.81,1:08:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.35,1:08:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.75,1:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to love swimming.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.94,1:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.44,1:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming was the only thing they would approve me to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.72,1:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't allowed on the team.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.31,1:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can swim.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.98,1:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.52,1:08:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Richard.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.56,1:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.36,1:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working a 12-step program,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.97,1:08:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've got a lot of material and background in the 12-step program.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.97,1:08:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.56,1:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a person's began to control the alcohol or the addiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.93,1:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Control what?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.84,1:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're no longer doing it for 20 years or so,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.88,1:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,yet the character defects continue to surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.97,1:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Any suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.77,1:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you keep doing the steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.21,1:09:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth step, third step, eleventh step.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.53,1:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Join other spiritual groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.97,1:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.84,1:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people on the 12-step do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.23,1:09:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the Course in Miracles, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.52,1:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you mean by character defect?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.64,1:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, promiscuity, things of this nature that...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.90,1:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, loss of impulse control?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.52,1:09:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.98,1:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're an impulse freak.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.39,1:09:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.81,1:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.13,1:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Addicted to impulsivity and instant gratification.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.09,1:09:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.22,1:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.13,1:09:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it takes a lot of purr.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.59,1:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.27,1:09:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.60,1:10:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.98,1:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try fasting.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.25,1:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can join a monastery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.53,1:10:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.23,1:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.10,1:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a form of addiction, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.84,1:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're addicted to sensation, pleasurable sensation.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.82,1:10:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.75,1:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is hope, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.17,1:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.50,1:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's lots of people that have grown beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.97,1:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.31,1:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.65,1:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people have grown beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.56,1:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep surrendering to God, praying,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.90,1:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and doing the best you can with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.56,1:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.56,1:10:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.28,1:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I came mostly for the hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.64,1:10:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.02,1:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.09,1:11:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned to the young gentleman earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.52,1:11:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that the use of a spiritual teacher can be very beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.67,1:11:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.86,1:11:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My question would be,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.93,1:11:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at what level should that teacher be at,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.64,1:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,whether in person or through a book?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.80,1:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody you relate to makes sense to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.38,1:11:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're too far beyond you,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.72,1:11:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it sounds too esoteric and unreal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.60,1:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they're behind you,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.77,1:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it sounds too simplistic, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.82,1:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you feel attracted to it, it's meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.09,1:11:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Vibrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.28,1:11:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be meaningful to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.44,1:11:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Informative and meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.06,1:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you sort of automatically gravitate to that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.47,1:11:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or their style is meaningful to you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.71,1:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And one teacher will appeal to a certain group
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.36,1:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and not appeal to another, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.18,1:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.60,1:11:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My style tends to be a little direct.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.31,1:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and not everybody goes through that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.50,1:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.84,1:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in enough time for their hearts and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.07,1:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd sometimes just go for the reality of it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.21,1:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.97,1:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You save 10, 20 lifetimes that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.43,1:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.92,1:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.97,1:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.47,1:12:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.39,1:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.73,1:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.85,1:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be the hug man on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.57,1:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once a touch-me-not.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.89,1:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.85,1:12:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I hated being physically near anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.07,1:12:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never have been on a good submarine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.18,1:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, some guy going by me, I'd go, Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.26,1:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As a kid, I couldn't stand the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.11,1:12:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was putting their grammy fingers in your eyes and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.61,1:12:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And rustling.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.92,1:12:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm a hug-a-bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.15,1:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.97,1:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was a touch-me-not, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.96,1:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.18,1:13:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.52,1:13:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.52,1:13:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.52,1:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.52,1:13:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the ways they've been helpful for me is to help me more consistently get past that
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.28,1:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,idea of an anthropomorphic God, which was really drummed into my head as a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.52,1:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.52,1:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we all did.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.52,1:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Through traditional Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.52,1:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.52,1:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,God of the Old Testament.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.52,1:13:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But then that raises a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.52,1:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you also, in your work, you emphasize praying and just letting go, submitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.52,1:13:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.52,1:13:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if there's not an anthropomorphic God to answer those prayers.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.52,1:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there could be a real God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.52,1:13:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, well, what's the mechanism?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.52,1:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the mechanism?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.52,1:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And how would prayer work?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.52,1:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we know it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.52,1:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it maybe through the attractor fields that you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.52,1:13:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something along those lines?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.52,1:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know about the mechanisms of prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.52,1:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.84,1:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the prayer itself, if you calibrate its energy, has an intention at a certain
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.15,1:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,level.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.15,1:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you surrender a thing to God, you don't look for a response, because you just
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.60,1:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendered it to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.60,1:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the prayer itself, if you calibrate its energy, has an intention at a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.60,1:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you surrender a thing to God, you don't look for a response, because you just
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.80,1:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendered it to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.80,1:14:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no anthropomorphic expectation.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.34,1:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.50,1:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking at a two-way communication.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.85,1:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to God that which surrenders itself to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.06,1:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and by so doing, you pull in the energy field of the infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.47,1:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I recommend the 91st Psalm.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.93,1:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that you hear a conversational answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.93,1:14:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that you come into the presence of a certain aha, knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.47,1:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, God, what is this all about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.60,1:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make head or tail out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.18,1:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.39,1:14:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, to heck with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.06,1:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get the paper, and you open it, and there it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.76,1:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.88,1:15:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.92,1:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an answer within the field, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.47,1:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.89,1:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you come to it because of the attraction of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.43,1:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so it is the attraction of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.92,1:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.43,1:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.02,1:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer unfolds of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.76,1:15:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the course of miracles, the way it's phrased is
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.85,1:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you ask the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.76,1:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.67,1:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A miracle means the recontextualization to your knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.36,1:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you automatically see the answer
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.05,1:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because that which is false is removed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.17,1:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're talking about the importance of contextualization,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.63,1:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that what looks wrong in this particular context,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.39,1:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in a different context, just lost its wrongness or its rightness.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.36,1:15:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.85,1:15:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer to that is,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.17,1:15:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I always look at step-down levels of divinity, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.89,1:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We said archangels are at 50,000 and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.71,1:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This planet, you can get about as far as 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.56,1:16:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, your nervous system burns out, and you croak.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.68,1:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We leave here at 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.61,1:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We seem very advanced.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.60,1:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in kindergarten in a level at archangel at 50,000
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.81,1:16:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're talking about logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.93,1:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I always see God's power as being infinite,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.50,1:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which you cannot handle.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.27,1:16:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't touch an infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.26,1:16:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant fry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.68,1:16:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's almost like step-down transformers, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.97,1:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this dimension and other dimensions,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.40,1:16:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you see levels of energy, levels of energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.93,1:16:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to 1,000, you don't see it on this planet anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.71,1:16:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean it's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.89,1:16:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You went into the celestial dimensions
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.72,1:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,where they start at 600 and up, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.76,1:16:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it advances to a nonverbal knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.39,1:16:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In the depths of hell, one eye said,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.39,1:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,well, not eye, but some voice,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.65,1:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and it said, in the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.96,1:17:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which is far worse than anybody's description of it I've ever read,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.76,1:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all hope forever, eternally beyond all hope,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.48,1:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the voice said, if there is a God, I ask him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.56,1:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.71,1:17:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, from the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.85,1:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly there was the realization of the allness of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.14,1:17:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that shone forth like, shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.60,1:17:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.84,1:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought, in the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.03,1:17:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,this prayer arose from some part of the consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.35,1:17:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and a passing archangel was cruising by,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.26,1:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed it, hmm, and left.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.88,1:17:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a hmm from an archangel.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.34,1:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I never spoke of it for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.81,1:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Silenced the mind for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.10,1:18:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Power beyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.39,1:18:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when the presence is in the form of,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.22,1:18:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.52,1:18:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a love that just melts you with its exquisiteness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.57,1:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That love has a peculiarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.53,1:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell people who've been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.88,1:18:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the meltingness is exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.40,1:18:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Also infinitely powerful and peculiarly like rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.19,1:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock-like.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.77,1:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.84,1:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Exquisitely gentle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.89,1:18:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the most powerful machine on earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.18,1:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.02,1:18:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In all dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.69,1:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Touches you, and it's like, whew.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.17,1:18:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Difficult to describe.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.53,1:18:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Softer than silk.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.53,1:18:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.81,1:19:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.06,1:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.64,1:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.64,1:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.64,1:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife, the Canadian, wanted you to sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.64,1:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.64,1:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife, the Canadian.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.64,1:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can get her over 415, I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.64,1:19:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I still got some Canadian money I've saved from my last trip there,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.64,1:19:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which was 35 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.64,1:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can still use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.64,1:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy it in my jewelry box.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.64,1:19:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.64,1:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Marta and Walter,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.64,1:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in Tucson?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.64,1:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anybody in Tucson.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.50,1:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.50,1:19:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a balancing program that had a lot of these same numbers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.75,1:19:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.75,1:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's common in the Hoonah, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.75,1:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Hoonah?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.75,1:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.75,1:19:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's good there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.75,1:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.75,1:19:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I love your common practicality in a field that's full of other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.75,1:19:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.75,1:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.75,1:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think spiritually it has to be real.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.75,1:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just airy-fairy out there someplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.77,1:19:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.77,1:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you do it when we all sit and meditate and play musical music
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.77,1:20:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and burn incense and flowers and do rose petals.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.77,1:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's not part of where you live.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.64,1:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day you're on the subway, you're dealing in business,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.64,1:20:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're dealing with children, wives, flat tires.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.64,1:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to have a spirituality that's real from moment to moment in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.64,1:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.64,1:20:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke about experiences in war being very transformational at times.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.69,1:20:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.69,1:20:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in Vietnam, and I came back after a year in the jungle, and I saw two people
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.98,1:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting for a parking place in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.98,1:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I swore I would never again get that upset over that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.98,1:20:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Happily, I never had to go to Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.65,1:20:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I volunteered, but they said over 70, they won't take you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.65,1:20:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have gladly had my place.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.57,1:20:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was a bloody war.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.84,1:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.94,1:21:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.94,1:21:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.97,1:21:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.38,1:21:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.09,1:21:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you live.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.09,1:21:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually I see you on my TV in France.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.09,1:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.09,1:21:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.09,1:21:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, are books being translated into French?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.09,1:21:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.09,1:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they translated?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.09,1:21:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.09,1:21:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.22,1:21:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.22,1:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the question is about water and its properties related to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.60,1:21:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these last years in the scientific community, people are demonstrating the ability
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.78,1:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of water to store information and to give it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.78,1:21:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a work of a Japanese person, Masaru Emoto, on the frozen water crystal
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.56,1:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that really brought love in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.56,1:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was right at the moment when you answered my question on Beyond the Ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.56,1:22:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,net radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.88,1:22:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And your answer was basically that I should not be passionate about thought systems and
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.26,1:22:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,theories.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.48,1:22:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the water crystal was kind of an answer to that, because it was just the overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.48,1:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.48,1:22:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't need to put a word on it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.57,1:22:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.64,1:22:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, I want to ask if it's beneficial for me to know something about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.64,1:22:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about water and consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.64,1:22:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,About water?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.64,1:22:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Water and consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.64,1:22:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is water a...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.64,1:22:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the effect of consciousness on crystals, water crystals.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.64,1:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, water crystals.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.64,1:22:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.64,1:22:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is water a condition for consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.64,1:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.64,1:22:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those experiments have been done for many years, not necessarily on the crystalline
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.64,1:22:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,structure of water, but on the surface tension, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.64,1:22:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can measure the surface tension, pray over it, and you change the surface tension
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.64,1:22:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the water, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.64,1:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.64,1:22:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.64,1:22:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's anecdotal.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.64,1:22:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it get you enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.64,1:22:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.64,1:22:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.64,1:22:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.64,1:22:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.64,1:22:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.64,1:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.64,1:22:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.64,1:22:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.64,1:22:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.73,1:22:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.73,1:22:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.73,1:22:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.73,1:23:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.73,1:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.73,1:23:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.73,1:23:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.73,1:23:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was one question that I wanted to gather so save your...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.76,1:23:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just diversion.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.76,1:23:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.76,1:23:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.76,1:23:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know if it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.76,1:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is water a condition for the expression of consciousness on earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.76,1:23:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.81,1:23:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.81,1:23:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Like everything you calibrated, they contain water.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.69,1:23:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.69,1:23:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to say, since we're...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.03,1:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to give some kind of a magical condition to water.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.84,1:23:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.84,1:23:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,W...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.84,1:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.84,1:23:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.11,1:23:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.38,1:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because your water and consciousness can affect the crystalline structure in the water, then so what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.43,1:23:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.61,1:23:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your physical body is going to stay here when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.38,1:23:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to take your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.56,1:23:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,These things demonstrating the effect of consciousness and its impact on the physical domain, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.85,1:23:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,are curiosities, but they are useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.97,1:24:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for instance, I can tell you, the Ganges River, which is one of the filthiest in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.23,1:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is the dumping ground of 100 cities, full of feces, dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.43,1:24:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River calibrates over 500, 510, 515, 510.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.31,1:24:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River calibrates at 510, which is higher than the water in your faucet at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.15,1:24:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.50,1:24:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.52,1:24:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Millions of faithful people praying, and what they did is they made the Ganges River sacred by intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.85,1:24:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Millions of Hindus over centuries and centuries have cleansed themselves in the Ganges and blessed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.85,1:25:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And in my lifetimes, as a worshiper of Shiva, I myself was incinerated on the ghats on the side of the Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.72,1:25:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ganges River...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.46,1:25:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River becomes its energy at 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.23,1:25:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.61,1:25:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But the water itself, I don't know anything about it, but I know of spiritual intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.23,1:25:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you bless food, you can calibrate food before you bless it, calibrate after you bless it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.77,1:25:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate food that's been made by hand with love at home, as compared to machine-made in the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.00,1:25:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.88,1:25:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see the impact of spiritual spirituality, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.34,1:25:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.60,1:25:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.68,1:25:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.30,1:25:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring upologizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.72,1:25:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you any while.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.00,1:25:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.18,1:25:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.27,1:25:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.39,1:25:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Casual.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.42,1:25:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to go after this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.53,1:25:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hopefully at an outreach topic.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.68,1:25:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would be useful, I think that's interesting, that the crystalline effect, crystalline expressions of water molecules are affected by consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.77,1:25:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.19,1:25:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sort of the Heisenberg principle, yeah, quantum mechanics of it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.23,1:26:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.53,1:26:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.21,1:26:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My body has been kind of puny this year, so I've had plenty of time to listen to your videos, and I've taken pieces and gotten them kind of mixed up, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.36,1:26:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And basically about prayer, if you pray for a specific result, you said at one point that's like telling God what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.19,1:26:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called outlining.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.19,1:26:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.19,1:26:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, I want $32 on Monday at 15, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.19,1:26:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have something specific that you want to have happen, it's like not surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.42,1:26:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then another time you said God doesn't interfere with Earth on any regard or on creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.55,1:26:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That he lets creation happen as the situation is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.55,1:27:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm kind of wondering, is prayer, besides communion, for any purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.96,1:27:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about prayer being used now as a blessing for food, for water, for rivers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.96,1:27:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a declaration of intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.96,1:27:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a certain energy of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.85,1:27:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We demonstrated today that it collapses the wave function from the viewpoint of quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.35,1:27:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is even a mathematics to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.72,1:27:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a statement of intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.72,1:27:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pray for God's will in a matter and surrender it to God, then you're not looking for an answer,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.63,1:27:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so you wouldn't know if you got one because you surrendered it already.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.63,1:27:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But the likelihood, the potentiality of that which is prayed for becomes higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.84,1:27:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know that that which you hold in mind tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.84,1:28:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never looked.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.42,1:28:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Never looked where to live the last three or four, five places I've lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.42,1:28:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I held in mind what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.09,1:28:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived way out in the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.09,1:28:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Went to many lectures, so many things in the city I thought if I just had an apartment in the city,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.09,1:28:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a little pita terre, you know, it'd be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.14,1:28:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I got in the car, drove into town, parked at a real estate agency,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.14,1:28:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,went in, said what I want on Fifth Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.39,1:28:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the only apartment available in all of New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.39,1:28:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rent controlled, right on Fifth Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.19,1:28:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.86,1:28:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just holding in mind the most, what you would be the most desire thing, but without adding desire to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.51,1:28:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.98,1:28:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you're not trying to force God to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.98,1:29:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whole different kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.98,1:29:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not really prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.98,1:29:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer is really surrendering your vision to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.94,1:29:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's karmically appropriate,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.94,1:29:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and divinity's in a good mood, it happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.52,1:29:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it's that nutty guy there with the same freaking prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.52,1:29:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you shut him up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.52,1:29:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They send you an email that says, Igne, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.17,1:29:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because so many things depend on karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.06,1:29:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See, and you don't know what the karmic evolution of that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.11,1:29:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So people say, I did this and this and this and this and nothing happened,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.11,1:29:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I quit doing anything and all of a sudden it happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.11,1:29:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You got yourself out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.35,1:29:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So surrendering is a continuous process.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.35,1:29:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.35,1:30:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, it's like a mudra where you consistently surrender as it appears to be happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.11,1:30:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever is, is whatever is.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.11,1:30:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.68,1:30:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You die today, you die ten years from now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.68,1:30:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.75,1:30:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.44,1:30:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.44,1:30:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll finish them all today.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.60,1:30:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.14,1:30:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.14,1:30:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have a, my question is always about daily life,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.14,1:30:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's hard to take this back.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.14,1:30:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-duality, trying to live your life in a state of non-duality
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.14,1:30:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,or not having positions about things, are we still supposed to vote?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.85,1:30:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You vote for the right one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.85,1:30:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I can calibrate and vote for the person who calibrates higher,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.85,1:31:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not necessarily...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.85,1:31:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you could do that if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.03,1:31:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But they both calibrate around the same, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.03,1:31:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm ultra-liberal.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.03,1:31:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That means they're all fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.44,1:31:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The collective karma of mankind is what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.44,1:31:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and its expression as America is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.44,1:31:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And what America needs to learn or go through or profit by will surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.44,1:31:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The people collectively will go in this way or that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.25,1:31:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I choose to vote, am I still participating in duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.85,1:31:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, duality is how you see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.85,1:31:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Duality is, you see, you would see it as a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.85,1:31:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Duality you'd see it as right and wrong and all kinds of judgmentalism and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.35,1:31:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.43,1:31:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, different drivers are going to have a different kind of ride, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.28,1:31:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With one, it seems a little prosaic, and the other could be quite exciting, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.28,1:32:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go this way today, that way tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.28,1:32:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm all for the excitement in whichever way it goes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.56,1:32:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Every president's been great.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.56,1:32:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is great in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.14,1:32:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I would have been bored with Hoover, however, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.00,1:32:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up in the time of Hoover, and he was sort of a boring kind of a guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.02,1:32:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have any questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.02,1:32:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've answered a lot of them for me,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.02,1:32:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanted to thank you so much for being who you are and sharing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.02,1:32:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.02,1:32:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to acknowledge your presence, too. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.02,1:32:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.02,1:32:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.02,1:32:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't say that about Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.63,1:32:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too young to appreciate his positive attributes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.14,1:32:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.17,1:32:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the era of prohibition, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.17,1:33:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was prohibition when I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.21,1:33:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody made bathtub gin.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.28,1:33:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.28,1:33:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying your books and listening to your tapes,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.28,1:33:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I understand that surrender and treating all actions as spiritual is critical,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.28,1:33:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but is that potentially incompatible or difficult with a career in business?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.28,1:33:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I spend 10, 12 hours a day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.28,1:33:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that compatible?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.28,1:33:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that compatible with what?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.28,1:33:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With a career in business, with, you know, focusing on, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.28,1:33:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're enjoying, making money and doing deals and things like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.28,1:33:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it very difficult to reconcile the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.28,1:33:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's because of the way you're contextualizing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.28,1:33:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you're contextualizing yourself as a profit maker which brings up guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.39,1:33:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or seeking profit or greed or, you know, you're contextualizing as guilty, greedy,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.39,1:33:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,solar plexus kind of a phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.39,1:33:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would look at your business more from the viewpoint of stewardship.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.39,1:33:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your responsibility is you have certain business gifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.69,1:34:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a lot of people in this world do not have the gifts to be a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.69,1:34:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to picture yourself as the steward of these gifts
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.47,1:34:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,from which everyone will benefit, employee, customer, co-worker,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.47,1:34:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you benefit the world by being the example of what that is
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.46,1:34:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and how that looks in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.46,1:34:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's lots of people that are interested
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.46,1:34:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in bringing spirituality into business.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.46,1:34:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They do so by integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.00,1:34:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity is very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.07,1:34:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity shows up on the bottom line.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.07,1:34:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the most integrous corporation in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.07,1:34:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Walmart?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.07,1:34:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Number uno.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.07,1:34:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Number uno.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.07,1:34:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.07,1:34:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I view business as, or anything that you might say,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.34,1:34:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I can't do kinesiology on that because that's selfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.34,1:34:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because you have a responsibility to your assets.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.34,1:34:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.34,1:34:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To the stewardship of your assets.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.34,1:35:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether they're, let's say you're born physically beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.34,1:35:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.34,1:35:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.34,1:35:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The best stewardship of that beauty might be to become a movie star
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.34,1:35:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or a singer or something where that asset brings joy and happiness to people.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.34,1:35:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So look at it more like the stewardship of your skills
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.39,1:35:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that you take responsibility that these skills are used
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.01,1:35:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best advantage of as many people as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.01,1:35:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, because of your integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.01,1:35:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the field will feed back to you whatever is the consequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.01,1:35:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about profit.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.01,1:35:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you, while you're doing things,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.61,1:35:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,are you thinking about each action being spiritual or whatever else?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.64,1:35:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you just have integrity and just do the best that you can?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.64,1:35:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You align yourself with integrity and make that your way of business.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.64,1:35:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where everything is win-win.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.64,1:35:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you're willing to karmically face the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.90,1:35:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Face God for the responsibility of your behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.90,1:36:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.47,1:36:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're aware at all times that you're karmically responsible
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.47,1:36:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,for the consequences of your choices and decisions and actions and words,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.47,1:36:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that acts as a constraint anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.47,1:36:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I teach, I'm very aware of the conscious,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.92,1:36:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the karmic responsibility of everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.92,1:36:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I write.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.52,1:36:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrate every word, every sentence, every chapter,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.59,1:36:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,every paragraph, every book.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.68,1:36:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't want to be the author of that which is false.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.68,1:36:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.00,1:36:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the commitment is integrity to the work itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.00,1:36:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the best that you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.00,1:36:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And being, let's say, a salesman,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.00,1:36:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then be the best salesman you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.00,1:36:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The best inventor, whatever it happens to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.59,1:36:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a hug too?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.59,1:36:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.17,1:37:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone should pick your gifts, whatever they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.17,1:37:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the steward of those gifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.43,1:37:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a mesomorphic body.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.43,1:37:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a high IQ.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.43,1:37:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's being good looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.43,1:37:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.22,1:37:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again also to Ed,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.89,1:37:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's accolades about all the work you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.89,1:37:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding kinesiology, I saw a video
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.89,1:37:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,where you had Susan repeat the mantra OM
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.89,1:37:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and it changed the outcome of the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.63,1:37:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that a person, personal agenda,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.77,1:37:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,can affect the work of kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.57,1:37:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the positionality affect the result?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.18,1:37:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The integrity of the question,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.18,1:37:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the integrity of the two people involved,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.18,1:37:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,will determine the likelihood of validity.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.18,1:38:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people ask me a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.85,1:38:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What they want me to do is to reinforce some positionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.85,1:38:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not really asking me a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.85,1:38:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're asking me to validate
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.85,1:38:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,some positionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.85,1:38:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question itself is not integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.18,1:38:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but can a person...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.92,1:38:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what integrity is?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.92,1:38:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.92,1:38:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It means surrounding the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.92,1:38:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,without having a positionality
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.94,1:38:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about how that should look or how it should come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.13,1:38:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But then if someone does...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.13,1:38:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they won't get correct answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.13,1:38:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.13,1:38:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one discern that that might be taking place?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.57,1:38:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.96,1:38:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's still a question,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.14,1:38:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,do you doubt your own sincerity and integrity?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.14,1:38:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.14,1:38:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then why would there be a question that means you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.14,1:38:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any doubt about the integrity of my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.39,1:38:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an absoluteness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.84,1:38:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as there's a doubt,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.90,1:39:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's some conflictual program,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.90,1:39:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you mean it about other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.15,1:39:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.15,1:39:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people have their own programs,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.96,1:39:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can only calibrate their level of integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.96,1:39:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and see that they get the same answer as you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.88,1:39:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who should you put faith in?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.88,1:39:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your question?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.00,1:39:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can a person's agenda...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.00,1:39:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it would decrease the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.00,1:39:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of their getting a correct response.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.00,1:39:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.00,1:39:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.35,1:39:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can that be discerned through kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.35,1:39:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this team doing it about this team?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.80,1:39:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.05,1:39:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If this team is integrous,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.05,1:39:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and their question would be,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.05,1:39:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,this team is reliable,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.05,1:39:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,they should get a correct answer, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.50,1:39:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody should get the same answer,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.50,1:39:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as integrity is intact.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.50,1:39:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,About whether this team is integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.31,1:39:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.31,1:40:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, everybody should get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.31,1:40:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're over 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.31,1:40:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then everybody should get,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.31,1:40:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, they're over 200, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.31,1:40:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, they should give up kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.31,1:40:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and do something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.31,1:40:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.31,1:40:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you accepting IOUs for hugs?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.31,1:40:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.31,1:40:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For hugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.31,1:40:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.31,1:40:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.35,1:40:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.35,1:40:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.52,1:40:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't quite understand the question
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.52,1:40:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you were phrasing it,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.52,1:40:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.09,1:40:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How reliable is reliable?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.09,1:40:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, pretty much sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.92,1:40:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but not always when it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.50,1:40:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing I'd like to say is thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.50,1:40:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.50,1:40:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of work for a lot of years.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.50,1:40:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.01,1:40:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm very appreciative of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.23,1:40:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And for those that don't know,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.23,1:40:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he recently had a birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.23,1:40:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.31,1:40:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.31,1:40:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the only birth the birth of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.42,1:41:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only death is the death of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.42,1:41:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.52,1:41:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,what we call birth, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.22,1:41:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is the emergence into the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.22,1:41:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and what we call death is leaving this physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.40,1:41:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So people identify it with physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.40,1:41:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In this lifetime experience at age three,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.07,1:41:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the physicality, as I told you,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.11,1:41:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,was a grave disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.11,1:41:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I personally had a lot of anger about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.11,1:41:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.11,1:41:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really pissed, but anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.11,1:41:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be the only thing
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.26,1:41:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be the death of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.26,1:41:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be the only death
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.26,1:41:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the death of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.86,1:41:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only experience one death.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.86,1:41:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical death you can't experience
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.56,1:41:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because the capacity to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.56,1:41:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,belongs to consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.56,1:41:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the minute it leaves the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.56,1:41:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that which has the capacity to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.56,1:41:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer part of the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.56,1:41:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't experience your own physical death.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.56,1:41:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only witness it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.56,1:42:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is love really the only reality in this dimension?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.17,1:42:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on who you ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.17,1:42:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna ask you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.17,1:42:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.17,1:42:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness of,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.42,1:42:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,no, the absolute reality is
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.71,1:42:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness of the oneness with
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.71,1:42:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.89,1:42:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as the absolute subjectivity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.89,1:42:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the knowingness of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.89,1:42:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.07,1:42:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,expressible
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.07,1:42:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as a quality of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.03,1:42:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be the primary presenting quality
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.03,1:42:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're coming from ordinariness,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.32,1:42:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then to go out into the presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.32,1:42:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the love that just blows you over.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.32,1:42:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you progress in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.31,1:42:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that condition of love begins to prevail,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.31,1:43:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so it doesn't knock you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.31,1:43:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you may next be aware
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.86,1:43:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of the incredible beauty of things,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.86,1:43:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and that beauty knocks you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.86,1:43:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the not being used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.86,1:43:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the quality itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.86,1:43:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.93,1:43:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,once you become aware of the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.93,1:43:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as all existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.96,1:43:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and see the beauty of all that exists,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.96,1:43:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then you don't get knocked out by it, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.96,1:43:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everything you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.96,1:43:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,when you first go into that state,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.89,1:43:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,these flowers would incapacitate me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.89,1:43:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to talk to you right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.07,1:43:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've gotten used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.07,1:43:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So the vibrant beauty of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.34,1:43:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the expression of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.34,1:43:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as the exquisite beauty of their presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.34,1:43:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I would learn how to live in that world.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.47,1:43:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But that took many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.47,1:43:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I left the city
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.72,1:43:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and said nothing really for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.72,1:43:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd give you a dollar,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.71,1:43:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd rather give you two dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.27,1:44:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and let me hug Sue.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.47,1:44:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my sword?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.88,1:44:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my sword?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.88,1:44:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's the buck I owe you for kissing her.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.09,1:44:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.53,1:44:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we're going to have to wrap it up, they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.53,1:44:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking at us with cold stares and threats.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.89,1:44:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So have we completed our answering everyone's questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.89,1:44:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do some words of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.21,1:44:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.21,1:44:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, well, today has been a wonderful day.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.23,1:44:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been my divine,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.65,1:44:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.19,1:45:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my pleasure to remain in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.11,1:45:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So as to be that which I am,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.39,1:45:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fullest extent that I can be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.39,1:45:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is my joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.52,1:45:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is my reward for being here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.27,1:45:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is being steward of one's gifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.28,1:45:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of looking for gain and gettingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.39,1:45:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which brings the energy down,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.47,1:45:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,brings guilt and limitation,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.47,1:45:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if we are completely, totally
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.47,1:45:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what we can be every moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.92,1:45:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we're fulfilling God's will for us,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.92,1:45:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we can live a guilt-free, joyful life.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.14,1:45:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest is God's problem, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.14,1:45:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're being the best tadpole you can be in the pond,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.23,1:45:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's what's more,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.23,1:45:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who can fault you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.23,1:45:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the best tadpole you can be from moment to moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.27,1:46:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I try to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.27,1:46:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I try to do it with this group.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.27,1:46:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, I'm always aware of the karmic responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.27,1:46:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the consequences because my vision goes back,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.27,1:46:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, beyond, well, through eternal,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.27,1:46:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what the world calls eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.27,1:46:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And one sees that every nuance,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.27,1:46:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,every movement has had,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.27,1:46:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,has a karmic consequence, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.34,1:46:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that enhances the appreciation of beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.63,1:46:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,radiates forth that beauty down the corridors of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.63,1:46:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one comes into the karmic inheritance of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.63,1:46:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,reverence for beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.63,1:46:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and in this lifetime it comes back to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.63,1:46:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and as I was saying to him,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.64,1:46:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when it first hits you, it sort of takes you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.84,1:46:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you get used to living in the Taj Mahal.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.84,1:46:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You get used to living in the Alhambra.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.77,1:46:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you learn how to function within the world again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.77,1:46:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it took many years,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.77,1:47:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why I came out here from New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.02,1:47:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I had an apartment at Fifth Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.27,1:47:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently visited New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.27,1:47:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a chance to see Central Park
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.27,1:47:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the places,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.27,1:47:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the Plaza Hotel for lunch and all the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.27,1:47:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was the lifestyle there,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.27,1:47:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,which couldn't be handled.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.27,1:47:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I left it for many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.27,1:47:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And now re-experienced it,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.27,1:47:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but from a whole different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.27,1:47:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I must say that people in New York City
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.27,1:47:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,are very loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.27,1:47:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Very loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.27,1:47:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very beautiful city.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.27,1:47:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course that's the way we experience all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.27,1:47:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What we can do for God
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.92,1:47:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is simultaneously what we can do for ourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.92,1:47:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To be all that we can be,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.92,1:47:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fullest extent we can be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.92,1:47:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.17,1:47:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, that was the message we got
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.84,1:47:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from God
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.42,1:48:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,at the beginning of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.64,1:48:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In a Chinese fortune cookie.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.64,1:48:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To be all that you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.93,1:48:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,From every moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.93,1:48:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you will never have any regret.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.93,1:48:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thank you all for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.93,1:48:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.46,1:48:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the dollars I made.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.46,1:48:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have made five, six of them.
